where the explosion occurred said two of the workers ran out of the 
alley engulfed in flames 
ive never seen anything like it before in my life she said 
their clothes were burned completely off and they were screaming 
for help 
kari eckert a private security guard who was one of the first 
people on the scene she said the injured woman yelled help me 
help me im on fire 
i turned around and i almost got sick ms eckert said i 
was scared to death 
