6yearold brother dropped a pistol and she was wounded in the neck 
and a 9yearold tampa boy was wounded by his 13yearold brother as 
they played with a handgun 
the orlando girl is not expected to be able to move or breathe on 
her own again the 9yearold tampa boy underwent surgery but is 
expected to recover 
martinez opposed including the gun legislation in his call for a 
special session on a 24 billion turnpike expansion plan but 
changed his mind last week as the accidents continued 
