being held in kabul and is reported in good condition the sources 
said 
at least three western correspondents and two foreign aid workers 
have been captured while traveling with the guerrillas all were 
released unharmed later 
obrien is the first american believed captured by afghans 
the rebels who call themselves islamic holy warriors have 
been fighting the sovietbacked kabul government for 11 years with 
help mainly from the united states and pakistan 
the soviet union ended nine years military involvement in the war 
on feb 15 but continues to arm president najibullahs government 
