films la strada amarcord films with more of a narrative 
structure 
this gave me the chance to leave that it liberated me more 
from stories psychologies situations conclusions 
true to his usual pattern fellini still has to make up the 
dialogue for the film it will be dubbed in in the months ahead as 
he cuts and edits the movie produced by mario and vittorio cecchi 
gori at a cost of about 14 million is due out in october 
fellini is working with several old collaborators including 
tullio pinelli who helped create the stories and screenplays of 
la strada and la dolce vita and dante ferretti who 
