bureau of labor statistics have dropped as low as 61 percent 
the muchmaligned rust belt starts with innate advantages built 
up over time and sometimes not appreciated until a company moves 
said j downs herold who manages the universitys industrial 
development research program 
what you have here are a lot of little tool and die shops and 
model makers herold said the amount of expertise that exists 
among these places in heattreating sandblasting the ability to 
bend and mold metals of all types thats an infrastructure you 
dont just start out and build 
