absorbed into the society system while trustcorp inc would be 
dissolved frederick teal chairman of societys bank in columbus 
ohio would become the new chief executive officer of trustcorp 
bank ohio 
society hasnt decided on a corporate name for trustcorp 
gillespie said 
its not our intention for trustcorp to become a branch office 
of a cleveland company we intend to run trustcorp of ohio as a 
standalone independent bank he said 
